"Los webhooks se configuran en **Studio** y esta configuración se divide "
"entre su :ref:`activador <studio/webhooks/webhook_trigger>` y sus "
":ref:`acciones <studio/webhooks/webhook_action>`."

#: ../../content/applications/studio/automated_actions/webhooks.rst:30
msgid ""
